<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A5500001" svcinfotypenbr = "01" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Precautions for Diagnosing Trouble
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Before using scan tool, read its “Operator’s (Instruction) Manual” to know how to use it.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM replacement
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
When substituting a known-good TCM, check that all relays and actuators have resistance of specified value.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Neglecting this check may result in damage to good TCM.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
